Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_review.model.manager

Class WolfReview

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_review.model.manager.WolfReview
public class WolfReview extends Object
This class is the main manager for the entire WolfReview system, it keeps track of multiple PaperTracks and provides methods to load tracks from a file, save tracks, add new tracks, and it ensures only one instance exists throughout the program
Author:
Steven Saleeb
